'''Fengel''' was the father of [[Indor (grandfather of Tuor)|Indor]] and a great-grandfather of [[Tuor]],<ref group="note">Tuor is called ''Turgon'' in this text.</ref> according to the early version of the [[legendarium]] in a prose fragment following ''[[The Book of Lost Tales]]''.<ref name=Fen>{{SM|P1}}, pp. 4-5</ref>

== Etymology ==
The name ''Fengel'' seems to be in [[Noldorin]], but its meaning is unclear.

An earlier name for the character was ''Eär''.<ref name=Fen/>

