== Other versions of the legendarium ==
=== Early legendarium ===
In the early [[legendarium]], the name ''Fengel'' was also used for two different characters at some point.

In ''[[The Lay of the Fall of Gondolin]]'', from c. [[1920]], ''Fengel'' replaced ''[[Peleg]]'' as the name of Tuor's father.<ref>{{LB|2c}}, p. 145</ref>

The name ''Fengel'' also appears as the name of Tuor himself, in a [[fragment of an alliterative Lay of Eärendel]] from c. [[1925]].<ref>{{LB|2b}}, p. 141</ref>

=== Later legendarium ===
In the later legendarium from ''[[The Lord of the Rings]]'', '''[[Fengel]]''' was the name of the fifteenth king of [[Rohan]].<ref>{{App|Mark}}, p. 1,069</ref>

